title: Policy3435(I)(A)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Regional School District 8 is committed to protecting its assets against the risk of loss or misuse. Accordingly, it is the policy of the Regional School District 8 to identify and promptly investigate any possibility of fraudulent or related dishonest activities against the District and, when appropriate, to pursue legal remedies available under the law.
